PROJECTS: 
Career_Connect Database System 
Centralized Job Application Interface: Career Connect functions as a centralized platform bridging job seekers 
and companies by integrating job listings, applications, and skill profiles in one unified system. It facilitates 
seamless communication between applicants and recruiters across various domains, simplifying the job search 
and hiring process. 
Dynamic Job Matching and Application Tracking: The portal enables applicants to create detailed profiles, tag 
skills, and explore job openings that match their expertise. It supports real-time job posting by companies and 
allows users to track their application statuses, enhancing transparency and reducing manual follow-ups. 
User-Friendly and Scalable Design: Developed with an intuitive interface and a normalized backend database, 
the system ensures a responsive user experience while handling high volumes of data. It supports secure 
authentication, efficient data retrieval, and role-based access for applicants and recruiters, promoting ease of 
use and operational efficiency. 
 
Online Shopping System: 
Comprehensive Digital Retail Platform: 
The Online Shopping System is a full-stack e-commerce solution designed to automate and optimize online retail 
operations. It integrates key functionalities such as user registration, product browsing, secure checkout, and 
order tracking. The platform effectively bridges the gap between customers and digital storefronts, offering a 
seamless and reliable shopping experience. 
Streamlined Backend Logic and Order Processing: 
Developed using Flask (Python) and MySQL, the system efficiently manages core modules including user 
authentication, product catalog management, cart functionality, order handling, and payment processing. The 
backend ensures accurate inventory tracking and secure transaction flow, while also supporting administrative 
control over sales, user accounts, and analytics. 
Responsive Interface and Scalable Architecture: 
Built with a responsive frontend using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, the system delivers an intuitive user 
experience across devices. The modular architecture and normalized relational database design promote 
maintainability and scalability, laying a strong foundation for enhancements such as personalized 
recommendations, performance analytics, and cloud-based deployment. 
 
Agriguru: 
Farmer-Buyer Connection Platform: AgriGuru serves as a digital interface that connects farmers with buyers, 
enabling farmers to list available crops and buyers to browse the listings in real-time, fostering direct 
communication between both parties. 
AI-Assisted Agricultural Guidance: The platform provides AI-powered support to farmers, offering tools to 
diagnose plant diseases, identify crop issues, and suggest the most suitable crops to irrigate based on real-time 
weather and seasonal conditions. 
Streamlined Communication & Crop Management: Farmers can directly interact with buyers for seamless 
transactions, while also receiving personalized guidance on crop care and management, optimizing both 
agricultural productivity and market access.
